{"tid":785043,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"露晒底【朗出沒】射極唔入累街坊　C朗幾乎做罪人","createTime":"2018-08-18T22:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T04:37:32.000Z","uid":147097,"like":52,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"70e103c6bae3a2e4b3a2e6cdf06f9ed7c22f0c94","tid":785043,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T22:41:22.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙巨星C朗拿度周日凌晨在意甲處子戰登場，為祖雲達斯披甲作客基爾禾，戰況峰迴路轉入球始起彼落，最終祖記憑補時3分鐘入波絕殺贏3比2，全取3分，但過程驚險，其中臨完場祖記本已入波，但因C朗犯規在先判詐胡，若然祖記最終未能獲勝，C朗就變成罪人。 <br />\n<br />\n祖記今仗開局順利，基迪拉開賽3分鐘為球隊先開紀錄，不過C朗遲遲未入局，未能擴大優勢，38分鐘基爾禾憑史迪賓斯基頭槌頂成1比1，下半場56分鐘祖記再輸12碼，基亞卓尼利操刀射成2比1反超前。 <br />\n<br />\nC朗開始上力，其中一次攻勢出大技，在3名敵衞看管下，禁區頂左路轉身勁射，被對方門將飛身擋出，75分鐘邦路斯接應角球頭槌爭頂，基爾禾馬迪亞巴尼擺烏龍，祖記追和2比2。 <br />\n<br />\n完場前祖記幾乎反超前，文迪蘇傑頭槌攻門，基爾禾後衞大腳清走，使用門線科技判定，皮球越過白界，當時球證判祖記入球有效，不過今次攻勢期間C朗懷疑犯手球，球證再使用VAR睇重播，認為C朗犯規在先，改判入球無效，基爾禾門將蘇蘭天奴亦受傷退下火線。 <br />\n<br />\n補時3分鐘，祖記今次真係入波，貝拿迪斯治近門撞入，祖記贏3比2完場，C朗終於笑番。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一早話左佢d入球數靠浪射堆出黎<br />\n<br />\n家下一離開皇馬即刻露晒底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屎上最佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班浪迷仲有乜好講<br />\n<br />\n以後佢有排柒 有排笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"6e6456870e39953e118f02f150b4a4d3a180e3f4","tid":785043,"uid":167777,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T22:46:31.000Z","msg":"唔係烏龍和埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff81a4e8585f84242ea312ebd261eb167be6197","tid":785043,"uid":13503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6e6456870e39953e118f02f150b4a4d3a180e3f4","tid":785043,"uid":167777,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T22:46:31.000Z","msg":"唔係烏龍和埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T23:06:56.000Z","msg":"意假用咁多錢買阿朗邊會比佢首場就輸波"},{"pid":"423f273478b11241fe4ff26cd87a678814cc697c","tid":785043,"uid":16451,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T23:14:00.000Z","msg":"好彩無續佢 尋晚廢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffd4e8b80ba1020bd885fbd39e1f15642a65435","tid":785043,"uid":55851,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T00:02:55.000Z","msg":"溫室小花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺曼聯靠朗尼，喺皇馬靠摩迪"},{"pid":"dbb7227253111d061912529cd56cd0d3b18d5e22","tid":785043,"uid":8572,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cffd4e8b80ba1020bd885fbd39e1f15642a65435","tid":785043,"uid":55851,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T00:02:55.000Z","msg":"溫室小花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺曼聯靠朗尼，喺皇馬靠摩迪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T00:03:36.000Z","msg":"呢度有大巴拿"},{"pid":"bce5d69026f3f17f97a139fe54ef3278e309317e","tid":785043,"uid":34572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T00:15:21.000Z","msg":"@王騎"},{"pid":"45c577e4a23a063ced196554ee2a4652870e357f","tid":785043,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T00:30:45.000Z","msg":"好在比哂錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152fb16bb2996dc5bf106dcebe64f30ceaf0